wiki.summary: "Tomboy" (stylized in all caps) is a song recorded by South Korean girl group (G)I-DLE for their first studio album, I Never Die. It was released as the album's lead single on March 14, 2022. The song marked the first release of (G)I-DLE as a quintet following the departure of member Soojin in August 2021. Read more on Last.fm.
